Cell["\<\
use input parameters to build a molecule. Start with addFirstMonomer, then \
addNextMonomer. If needed, add special bonds such as a fused ring using \
addToPotential.
Format: addNextMonomer[{newpdb_,newitp_},{an_,bn_,cn_},Ores_,{ao_,bo_,co_},\
lBond_,phi_]
For long chains of complex copolymers, use pMon to keep track of indexing.\
\>", "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.885899054770514*^9, 3.885899148170721*^9}, {
  3.933328814610331*^9, 3.933328864347598*^9}, {3.93333014648114*^9, 
